Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Customer
  • public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
    Customer Class is to handle the information of customer so that the program can access them easily. A Customer object should contain the following private members: String Cust_username - The customer's username, String Cust_password - The customer's password, String Cust_fullname - The customer's fullname, String Cust_phonenum - The customer's phone number, String Cust_status - The customer's status [could be normal/case/close]
